01 CLAIM-LINE PIC X(512).
FD POLICIES-FILE.
01 POLICY-LINE PIC X(256).
FD DIAG-FILE.
01 DIAG-LINE PIC X(128).
FD FAC-FILE.
01 FAC-LINE PIC X(128).
FD DECK-FILE.
01 DECK-LINE PIC X(256).
FD REJ-PREC-FILE.
01 REJ-PREC-LINE PIC X(128).
FD REV-PREC-FILE.
01 REV-PREC-LINE PIC X(128).
FD BANK-FILE.
01 BANK-LINE PIC X(256).
FD PRIOR-LED-FILE.
01 PRIOR-LED-LINE PIC X(256).
FD OUT-LED-FILE.
01 OUT-LED-LINE PIC X(256).
FD DECISIONS-FILE.
